{"tid":246124,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"聽聞sony z5p 經常會耳機接觸不良","createTime":"2017-05-16T18:03:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-17T16:24:39.000Z","uid":92315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5885f5c0e6c07095a21e606a7a207460b4cec7fe","tid":246124,"uid":92315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T18:03:52.000Z","msg":"有冇人試過同樣情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n左上角冇咗耳機圖示<br />\n一時耳機出聲一時喇叭出<br />\n播片會不斷暫停<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\ngoogle見到z5p經常有耳機接觸不良<br />\n請問去返sony整大約要幾耐同幾錢？<br />\n係咪去佢哋旺角間中心搞？"},{"pid":"5f8ba9e9f065db02ed17da00d6de2b5c98a8e152","tid":246124,"uid":91325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T18:07:00.000Z","msg":"受害者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好彩果陣未過保養拎左去sony整"},{"pid":"da829ffa8b2e92eef3ce63c92b1fc2099c96cb23","tid":246124,"uid":92315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T18:11:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>受害者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好彩果陣未過保養拎左去sony整</blockquote><br />\n過咗保，心知不妙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb854996b032ca24ff9bb6e48c3f56086c956843","tid":246124,"uid":3527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T18:44:06.000Z","msg":"受害者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n買咗3個月唔夠已經detect 唔到耳機，身邊有2個fd 同樣情況，未過保拎去整好似1換1 <br />\nP.S. 聽fd講，我果部未得閒拎去整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d263c9ee6e4679ad3c3fbde4b17604ad87f1b385","tid":246124,"uid":71020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T18:48:06.000Z","msg":"放棄左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家用藍牙，反正唔係成日聽歌"},{"pid":"b9a6636c2a61e9489905b4f97706ac9907db620b","tid":246124,"uid":92315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"c